                Fortu&amp;lt;n=M&amp;gt;ae <expan><abbr>Reg</abbr><ex>inae</ex></expan> <lb n="2"/>duci MA<supplied reason="lost"><gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/></supplied>NAE <expan><abbr>coh</abbr><ex>ortis</ex></expan> <lb n="3"/>II <expan><abbr>pr</abbr><ex>aetoriae</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>p</abbr><ex>iae</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>v</abbr><ex>indicis</ex></expan> <del rend="erasure">Maximinia</del><lb break="no" n="4"/>nae <expan><abbr>cura</abbr><ex>m</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>agent</abbr><ex>ibus</ex></expan> <lb n="5"/>|(centurionibus) <expan><abbr>coh</abbr><ex>ortis</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>upra</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>criptae</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>mil</abbr><ex>itum</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Bri</abbr><ex>ttonum</ex></expan> <lb n="6"/>et <del rend="erasure"><expan><abbr>Osrhoenor</abbr><ex>um</ex></expan></del> I <lb n="7"/>BOPTO<supplied reason="lost"><gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/></supplied>BONVAE <lb n="8"/>VREC<gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>NOVEN <lb n="9"/>F<gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>inte <lb n="10"/><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>atia <lb n="11"/><supplied reason="lost">a</supplied>ram <supplied reason="lost">po</supplied>suit <lb n="12"/><supplied reason="lost">de su</supplied>o pro salute eo<lb break="no" n="13"/>rum 
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Die Inschrift wurde größtenteils flüchtig abgearbeitet. Autopsie R. Wiegels. (B): CIL 13, 06677a add. 04, p. 107; Ésperandieu: Z. 2 (Mitte): aeternae; Ésperandieu: Z. 6: [[Osrhoen]]o[[r(um)]]; Frenz: Z. 6: [[Osrhoeno]]r(um) i. Auf der linken Nebenseite eine Pflanze, auf der rechten ein Altar mit Opferschale und einem Fisch darin dargestellt.</p>
            </div>
